datasets::mtcars, factored and labeled

Source: R/erikmisc_DATA.R
dat_mtcars_e.Rd

Using datasets::mtcars, then applying labeled factors and labeling variables with labelled::var_label based on ?datasets::mtcars

data(dat_mtcars_e)

Format

tibble

Source

?datasets::mtcars

Examples

data(dat_mtcars_e)
str(dat_mtcars_e)
